		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I saw this - it looks really interesting.<br /><br />Also interesting is the fact that most of the game was written in C. I was under the impression that anything of this relative complexity would've required more hand-tuned assembly.<br />I'm eager to look through the source, though.

		

